{"tid":49894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【九龍塘墮軌】躺路軌凹位保命 列車底救出墮軌女","createTime":"2016-12-22T04:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T05:56:17.000Z","uid":426,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8608c7748b0588342fa54ccc72b0ea932f4ecd9","tid":49894,"uid":426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54r35H1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54r35H1.jpg&h=6605904e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【12：25更新】新增影片東鐵九龍塘站往上水方向的月台，今早發生女乘客墮軌奇蹟生還獲救事件。該名女乘客在月候車期間意外墮軌，當時一列北上的東鐵列車經已駛入月台，車長即時煞車至月台中央位置停下，但已經過了女事主墮軌位置，幸她剛躺在路軌中央凹䧟位置，列車未有輾過其身體。<br />\n<br />\n消防員接報到場拯救，在列車底部路軌中央的凹陷位置，發現受傷女事主，於是設法將她救出，最後在兩卡列車之間的空檔位置，將女乘客救離列車底部，再將她抬上南行線月台，由擔架床送院治理。女乘客獲救出時，血流披臉，衣服沾滿污漬，傷勢頗為嚴重。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161222&amp;guid=56077844&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161222%26guid%3D56077844%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=VgOsMrzToc1whm0geNSfcwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=1b30b372\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161222%26guid%3D56077844%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=faea4277\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161222&amp;guid=56077844&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"1a8bbc46c22a2fabf0543c018eb1ea029eab304e","tid":49894,"uid":16239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfa90d49b4c6f3744647eb1064ed0bb71034bc7","tid":49894,"uid":426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T04:46:42.000Z","msg":"諗起Gantz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"